00:04:24.206 --> 00:04:26.626 A:middle
But, Transit is not limited to

00:04:26.626 --> 00:04:27.256 A:middle
China alone.

00:04:28.306 --> 00:04:29.556 A:middle
You can use Apple Pay to ride

00:04:29.596 --> 00:04:30.736 A:middle
