However, we're heard that the

00:06:27.296 --> 00:06:28.606 A:middle
button does not always fit all

00:06:28.606 --> 00:06:30.476 A:middle
of your needs, and so today,

00:06:30.706 --> 00:06:31.936 A:middle
we're announcing three new types

00:06:31.936 --> 00:06:32.586 A:middle
in iOS 12.

