checkout performs Apple Pay.

00:07:14.256 --> 00:07:15.806 A:middle
That's not all the changes to

00:07:15.806 --> 00:07:16.176 A:middle
the button.

00:07:17.216 --> 00:07:18.736 A:middle
You know that we love rounded

00:07:18.736 --> 00:07:20.016 A:middle
corners and continuous curves,

00:07:20.526 --> 00:07:21.496 A:middle
but we understand that not

00:07:21.496 --> 00:07:22.496 A:middle
everybody shares exactly the

00:07:22.496 --> 00:07:24.316 A:middle
same feelings, and so this year,

00:07:25.006 --> 00:07:26.026 A:middle
we're allowing you to control

00:07:26.026 --> 00:07:28.956 A:middle
the corner edits of the button.

00:07:29.126 --> 00:07:30.506 A:middle
You can configure this however

00:07:30.506 --> 00:07:32.066 A:middle
you see fit to match existing

00:07:32.066 --> 00:07:33.926 A:middle
styles of your apps or websites.

