The new types and corner radius

00:07:55.616 --> 00:07:56.746 A:middle
are available in iOS 12 today.

00:07:56.836 --> 00:07:58.156 A:middle
And, they're coming to WebKit in

00:07:58.156 --> 00:07:58.896 A:middle
a future release.

00:08:00.186 --> 00:08:01.856 A:middle
Most importantly, fallback to

00:08:01.856 --> 00:08:03.706 A:middle
using older types on unsupported

00:08:03.706 --> 00:08:04.166 A:middle
versions.

00:08:04.696 --> 00:08:05.756 A:middle
Consider that cascade.

